name: Cardology Mix
description:
Description

Sharing this because I've gotten a few requests for links. There are some similar models on the site already but it's fun to create your own "style", and to tweak this or that. I may upload multiple version. It's a semi-chibi mix with an artstyle anime and western animation, and it mixes decently with other LoRAs.

This series started with the recipe for AbyssHellMaple but has changed a lot since then. The name was because I was gonna use it for a card-based project at some point.

I really wanted a specific skin texture and I'm glad I could achieve it. It always reminded me of cookie dough for some reason.

Usage

Do whatever pretty much. You can reference the preview images for my usual settings. I recommend the VAE from AbyssOrangeMix3. It mixes pretty well with most character and style LoRAs. Backgrounds are pretty weak in v4 so you'll need to describe them more in your prompts.

Note: Civitai messes up parsing the negatives in the preview images due to an extension. Just remove the duplicate stuff from the regular prompt. ezpz

Components

I'm really annoyed when mixes don't share what goes into them. If you enjoy this model please give the authors some love. Basically I had a few different categories of models in mind when picking LoRAs to merge. v4 uses these

Base Model

  • AbyssOrangeMix3 (Use the VAE as well)

Chibi / Cute

  • Maplestory

  • PastelKa

  • Yaro

  • Yuzusoft Chibi

Squishable Faces

  • aaaa

  • Yudeebi

General Style

  • Helltaker

  • Takamichi

  • Pixar

Each have a mix weight of between 0.1 and 0.4. I found adding a 3d render based lora (pixar in v4) really cleans things up.
